 srcSet=\"/static/d3148445307114ef7dab9c67f1d64fb0/a1fde/babes_logo.png 74w,\n/static/d3148445307114ef7dab9c67f1d64fb0/e1a69/babes_logo.png 149w,\n/static/d3148445307114ef7dab9c67f1d64fb0/17353/babes_logo.png 297w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 297px) 100vw, 297px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 297px) 100vw, 297px\" srcSet=\"/static/d3148445307114ef7dab9c67f1d64fb0/a1fde/babes_logo.png 74w,\n/static/d3148445307114ef7dab9c67f1d64fb0/e1a69/babes_logo.png 149w,\n/static/d3148445307114ef7dab9c67f1d64fb0/17353/babes_logo.png 297w\" src=\"/static/d3148445307114ef7dab9c67f1d64fb0/17353/babes_logo.png\" alt=\"Babe&#x27;s Old Fashioned Food Logo\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/d3148445307114ef7dab9c67f1d64fb0/a1fde/babes_logo.png 74w,\n/static/d3148445307114ef7dab9c67f1d64fb0/e1a69/babes_logo.png 149w,\n/static/d3148445307114ef7dab9c67f1d64fb0/17353/babes_logo.png 297w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 297px) 100vw, 297px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 297px) 100vw, 297px\" srcset=\"/static/d3148445307114ef7dab9c67f1d64fb0/a1fde/babes_logo.png 74w,\n/static/d3148445307114ef7dab9c67f1d64fb0/e1a69/babes_logo.png 149w,\n/static/d3148445307114ef7dab9c67f1d64fb0/17353/babes_logo.png 297w\" src=\"/static/d3148445307114ef7dab9c67f1d64fb0/17353/babes_logo.png\" alt=\"Babe's Old Fashioned Food Logo\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nThe PM Group is excited to announce that Babe’s Old Fashioned Food has joined our agency family! Babe’s has been locally owned and operated in San Antonio since 1987 and now has four locations throughout the city.  They pride themselves on made-from-scratch, mouth-watering old fashioned food like tasty hamburgers, hand cut fries, and homemade chicken tenders.  We look forward to serving up delivious new marketing ideas for Babe’s!<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<strong><u><a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com\">About The PM Group</a>:</u></strong> The PM Group was founded in 1988. Over the past 30 years, the agency has continued to grow and is currently listed as San Antonio’s Largest Advertising Agency by the <em>San Antonio Business Journal</em>. The PM Group’s client roster spans numerous industries including automotive, CPG, entertainment and sports marketing, legal, business services, non-profit, real estate and fitness. In addition, the agency hosts an annual Charity Gala every February that to date has raised over $2.5 million for local San Antonio area non-profit organizations in the last 15 years!  It is our way of giving back to the community that we so humbly serve.</p>\n","title":"The PM Group Adds New Restaurant Client to Agency Family","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"The PM Group Adds New Restaurant Client to Agency Family","url":"/the-pm-group-adds-new-restaurant-client-to-agency-family/"}],"title":"New Client - Babe's Old Fashioned Food | The PM Group","metaDesc":"The PM Group is excited to announce that Babe's Old Fashioned Food, a locally owned and operated burger joint, has joined our agency family!","focuskw":"babes","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"New Client - Babe's Old Fashioned Food | The PM Group","opengraphDescription":"The PM Group is excited to announce that Babe's Old Fashioned Food, a locally owned and operated burger joint, has joined our agency family!","opengraphImage":{"altText":"Babe's Old Fashioned Food Logo","sourceUrl":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/babes_logo-1.png","srcSet":null},"twitterTitle":"","twitterDescription":"","twitterImage":null,"canonical":"/the-pm-group-adds-new-restaurant-client-to-agency-family/","cornerstone":false,"schema":{"raw":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@graph\":[{\"